org.apache.http.client

接口 AuthCache

  • 所有已知实现类:
    BasicAuthCache

    public interface AuthCache
    Abstract AuthScheme cache. Initialized AuthScheme objects from this cache can be used to preemptively authenticate against known hosts.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.1
